           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se errori                           *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        p-rsc                not  = spaces
                     go to prn-rou-pri-900.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
